CREATE TABLE customers (

  full_name VARCHAR(255),
  email VARCHAR(255),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  price DECIMAL(10,2)
);

  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  rating INT,

  FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(id),

);

  status VARCHAR(10) DEFAULT 'pending',
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(id)
);
